back tomorrow. PENDING CASE.','10/5/11 Joy Arenas [joy@outsource2northstar.com]\r\n\r\nHi Melvin,\r\nWe were able to callback this customer today and clarify the issue as to why his installation didn’t push through on the CRD.  We apologized for the inconvenience that we caused him and tried to salvage the sale  however, customer is already closed minded and don’t want to proceed with his MIO TV application.\r\n\r\nFYI. Case closed.','PENDING','10/5/11 Kwong Jie Hui Melvin [melvinkjh@singtel.com]\r\n\r\nHi Joy,\r\n\r\nNoted.\r\n\r\nHi Santhi,\r\n\r\nFYI.\r\n\r\nMelvin Kwong',NULL,'2011-10-12 17:02:49'),(591,239,17,NULL,NULL,'NEW',NULL,NULL,NULL),(592,239,17,'10/3/11 Joy Arenas [joy@outsource2northstar.com]\r\n\r\nHi Melvin,\r\n\r\nThis case has been closed from our end 29 June and the resolution was, to revert back the package from Ultimate Pack to the Regular Sports Pack. \r\n\r\nPlease see attached email exchanges between Arthur and Linda back then. Also, attached is the recordings when we made the call back to the customer informing her that Ultimate Package will be replaced by Sports pack only.\r\n****\r\nFrom: arthur layos [mailto:arthur@outsource2northstar.com] \r\nSent: Wednesday, June 29, 2011 2:18 PM\r\nTo: Linda Ling\r\n\r\nHi Linda, \r\n\r\nBefore we call back this customer we listened to the Sales call below scenarios on the conversation: \r\n\r\n- Our Staff  was able to talk and closed the deal  with the husband MUHAMAD ISKANDAR (S8108006B), called on the mobile # on the lead 92318249 because his wife is not available. \r\n\r\n- Our Staff confirmed that the customer is subscribed to BPL for the last season; customer said yes. Rep asked if he is still interested to subscribe for this season of BPL; customer said yes, he is interested. \r\n\r\n- Our Staff offered Ultimate pack ($49.90) with 50% off for the first 3 months ($24.95). Staff explained that it will include BPL and the rest of the sports channel and entertainment channels. - Customer said that h